    <div class="section-heading"><span class="section-number">VI.</span> Client's Duties and Cooperation</div>

    <p class="clause">
        The Client agrees to fully cooperate with the Firm throughout the course of the representation,
        including but not limited to the following obligations:
    </p>
    <ul class="clause-list">
        <li><b>Communication:</b> Promptly respond to all communications from the Firm within three (3) business days;</li>
        <li><b>Honesty:</b> Provide complete, truthful, and accurate information at all times;</li>
        <li><b>Medical Treatment:</b> Follow through with all recommended medical treatment and provide the Firm with updated treating provider information;</li>
        <li><b>Documentation:</b> Provide all documents, photographs, records, and evidence relevant to the case promptly upon request;</li>
        <li><b>No Independent Contact:</b> Refrain from independently contacting opposing counsel, insurance adjusters, or any party adverse to Client's interests without prior written approval from the Firm;</li>
        <li><b>No Social Media:</b> Refrain from posting any information about the incident, injuries, or case on any social media platform;</li>
        <li><b>Address Changes:</b> Notify the Firm immediately of any change in address, phone number, or email address;</li>
        <li><b>Court Appearances:</b> Appear at all depositions, hearings, mediations, and court proceedings as required;</li>
        <li><b>Settlement Authority:</b> Client has the sole authority to accept or reject any settlement offer. The Firm will communicate all offers and provide recommendations, but the final decision rests with Client.</li>
    </ul>

    <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
         ATTORNEY'S DUTIES
    ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <div class="section-heading"><span class="section-number">VII.</span> Attorney's Duties</div>

    <p class="clause">
        The Firm agrees to perform the following in connection with Client's representation:
    </p>
    <ul class="clause-list">
        <li>Diligently investigate, prepare, and pursue Client's claim;</li>
        <li>Keep Client reasonably informed of all significant case developments;</li>
        <li>Promptly respond to Client's communications within three (3) business days;</li>
        <li>Exercise independent professional judgment in Client's best interest;</li>
        <li>Maintain Client communications and case records in strict confidence;</li>
        <li>Provide Client with a written accounting of all fees and costs upon request or at case conclusion;</li>
        <li>Promptly disburse Client's share of any recovery after deducting fees and costs.</li>
    </ul>

